<html lang='en'>
  {{> partials/head }}
  {{> partials/scripts }}
  <script type='text/javascript'>
    let captcha; var onloadCallback = function() { captcha =
    grecaptcha.render('custom-captcha', { 'sitekey' :
    '6Le2Iz8nAAAAAGMG3_CaDs3o_Z1o34KMuhFjrAHc' }); };
  </script>
  <body class='about-us'>
    {{> partials/nav}}
    <header>
      <div class='header-content'>
        <div class='text-half'>
          <h1>Turning Returns into Strategic Decisions</h1>
          <p class='subtitle'>
            With Skila, leverage the power of return analytics to uncover hidden
            insights, optimize product performance, and drive impactful business
            strategies.
          </p>
          <div class='image-half'>
            <img src='/assets/images/table_people.png' />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main>
      <div class='background'>
        <section id='why'>
          <div class='section-wrapper no-padding-bottom'>
            <div class='text-center'>
              <h2>Spare yourself the headache</h2>
              <p>With Skila you can simplify the return process while
                transforming it into a source of valuable insights. These
                insights empower businesses to improve their product design and
                functionality, and enhance customer satisfaction, ultimately
                leading to a more successful and customer-centric business.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='section-wrapper no-padding-top'>
            <div class='form-content section-padder'>
              <div class="section-padder">
                <h1>Ready to get your free trial?</h1>
                <p class='subtitle'>
                  Create your free account without any hassle and use the Skila
                  platform.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <form
                  id='trial-form-id'
                  class='trial-form'
                  data-netlify-recaptcha='true'
                  data-netlify='true'
                >
                  <h2>Sign up for a free trial</h2>
                  <div class='form-element'>
                    <div class='form-element first-name'>
                      <input
                        required
                        name='firstName'
                        placeholder='First name'
                      />
                    </div>
                    <div class='form-element last-name'>
                      <input required name='lastName' placeholder='Last name' />
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class='form-element'>
                    <input
                      type='email'
                      required
                      name='email'
                      placeholder='Email address'
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class='form-element'>
                    <input
                      required
                      name='password'
                      minlength='8'
                      type='password'
                      placeholder='Create password'
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class='form-element'>
                    <input
                      required
                      name='companyName'
                      placeholder='Company name'
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class='form-element'>
                    <input required name='region' placeholder='Region' />
                  </div>
                  <div class='form-element'>
                    <input
                      required
                      name='shopifyStore'
                      placeholder='Shopify store'
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class='form-element'>
                    <select
                      required
                      name='product'
                      id='productSelect'
                      placeholder='Select product of interest'
                    >
                      <option value='' disabled selected>Select product of
                        interest</option>
                      <option value='ship'>Ship</option>
                      <option value='track'>Track</option>
                      <option value='return'>Return</option>
                      <option value='allOfTheAbove'>All of the above</option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                  <div id='custom-captcha'></div>
                  <div class='form-element'>
                    <button
                      loading
                      class='button primary'
                      type='submit'
                      name='submitButton'
                    >Register</button>
                  </div>
                  <div class='form-element'><span class='footer-text'>By
                      submitting this form, you agree to Skilaâ€™s
                      <a class='inline-link' href='/privacy.html'>Privacy Policy</a>,
                      and you consent to receive personalized marketing
                      communications.</span></div>
                </form>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
      <div class='background smaller-background margin-top'>
        <section id='why-2'>
          <div class='section-wrapper'>
            <div class='stock-image'>
              <img src='assets/images/skila_woman_banner_low_1.png' />
            </div>
            <div class='section-padder text-center'>
              <h2>Track your devices from the begining of their journey</h2>
              <p>Begin the journey with your devices right from the start.
                Utilize Skila to efficiently track your devices, keeping a
                vigilant eye on their journey from the moment they are
                dispatched. Skila's advanced tracking capabilities provide
                comprehensive visibility into your product's life cycle. By
                tracking the life cycle, you can understand when and why returns
                happen, enabling you to make strategic decisions about product
                improvements. With Skila, turn your product life cycle tracking
                into a strategic advantage.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
      <section id='why-3'>
        <div class='section-wrapper'>
          <div class='section-padder text-center'>
            <div class='card-container'>
              <div class='card-icon'>
                <img src='assets/images/express-delivery-1.svg' />
              </div>
              <div class='card-icon'>
                <img src='assets/images/tracking-1.svg' />
              </div>
              <div class='card-icon'>
                <img src='assets/images/return-box-1.svg' />
              </div>
            </div>
            <h2>Easy integration with all major carriers</h2>
            <p>Discover the range of carriers compatible with Skila, your
              reliable partner for efficient product delivery. We proudly
              integrate with major carriers including GLS, FedEx, DPD, and DHL,
              USPS, ensuring your goods reach your customers swiftly and
              securely. Leveraging Skila's robust system, you can utilize these
              carrier services, each offering a unique blend of benefits, to
              cater to the diverse needs of your customer base. Explore the
              unparalleled flexibility and power of Skila to optimize your
              shipping process and enhance customer satisfaction.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <div class='background'>
        <section id='why-4'>
          <div class='section-wrapper'>
            <div class='section-padder text-center'>
              <h2>Our carrier partners</h2>
              <div class='icon-container'>
                <img
                  src='assets/images/dhl_logo_white.svg'
                  class='carrier-icon'
                />
                <img
                  src='assets/images/us_postal_service_logo_white.svg'
                  class='carrier-icon'
                />
                <img
                  src='assets/images/ups_logo_white.svg'
                  class='carrier-icon'
                />
                <img
                  src='assets/images/gls_logo_white.svg'
                  class='carrier-icon'
                />
                <img
                  src='assets/images/fedex_logo_white.svg'
                  class='carrier-icon'
                />
                <img
                  src='assets/images/dpd_logo_white.svg'
                  class='carrier-icon'
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>
    {{> partials/footer }}
    <script
      src='https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js?onload=onloadCallback&render=explicit'
      async
      defer
    >
    </script>
  </body>
</html>